{"type": "article", "id": 40832, "title": "猫主子，你可看得上这个新窝？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-15T23:05:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 9401, "name": "Monkey Business"}, {"id": 40438, "name": "MoNi Studio"}, {"id": 40439, "name": "clé"}, {"id": 40440, "name": "Design Bridge"}, {"id": 40441, "name": "Fortnum & Mason"}, {"id": 40442, "name": "Parallel"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 124, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170516070511UJKdCP9fG8HVWjD5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Easiseat by MoNi Studio</h3><p>我们都知道轮椅可以让老人和伤残人士更方便地出行，但在日常生活中它们使用起来并不方便。为了照顾患有渐冻症的母亲，香港设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/moni.design.studio/\" rel=\"nofollow\">MoNi Studio</a> 的创始人 KT Chun 曾在市面上寻找能让母亲自主操控的电动轮椅或是便椅，在发现同类产品无法满足需求后，他带领团队研发了这款可以无线遥控的轮椅“随席”。“随席”不仅可以横向或是斜向移动，还可以在狭小的空间内完成 360 度自转。在用户上厕所的时候，只要将身体固定在配套的皮带上，可升降的椅背会根据需要调整位置，让他们有机会重拾自主生活。因为明白很多轮椅使用者相当在意他人的目光，Chun 对“随席”的外观也进行了一番改良，让它更像是一款多功能的木制家具。目前，“随席”已在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1084164788/easiseat-an-innovative-furniture-for-disabled-pers/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kickstarter</a> 上集资成功，单价从 26800 港币起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221035nejMkrgCv1LAZWaU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221036nTVd30YGeczmwytW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.939706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221035b4pW0HUJXtgYA73C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221035wUxXDQzibAZ72Ss6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.389706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221036VwsAdDpGNi7nK4jI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Cone by WISKI</h3><p>和其他猫奴设计师一样，猫用家具品牌 <a href=\"https://wiskicat.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">WISKI</a> 的创始人 Evan Ryan 也是在找不到让自己满意的同类产品后产生了亲自设计的想法。最近，他推出了这款结合了猫窝和猫抓柱功能的家具 Cone，包裹在外的剑麻罩可以随时拆卸，团队估计最长可供一只喵星人使用五年的时间。它的顶部还配有一个把手，移动起来非常方便。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/wiskicat/the-cone-by-wiski-scratch-beautifully\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 185 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221051qIs5Abj7ci84vH9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772059\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221052D6COypmw312Fqv8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221051Ijwe8YsaV1qvyWl4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221051tih3ORMWUEJSwGyZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Gifted by Monkey Business</h3><p>不擅长包装礼物或是打蝴蝶结？来自以色列产品设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Monkey Business</a> 的这套 Gifted 硅胶带可以助你一臂之力，只要轻轻一套，就可以把任何物品打包成一件礼物。每套 Gifted 由五种颜色组成，分为 5 厘米和 8 厘米两种尺寸，共 10 条。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.mnkbusiness.com/gifted-multicolour/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 10 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705152211146LjIuTSZsN5EvJlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221114zv1ZuBdsrCpF9P7t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.152812\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705152211144gNHehzr1waEpbLt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.123472\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tides Collection by clé</h3><p>由美国设计师 Deborah Osborn 创立的 <a href=\"https://www.cletile.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">clé</a> 是一个由艺术家和工匠组成的瓷砖品牌，产品的风格相当多元并且充满了艺术气息。最近，Deborah Osborn 的儿子、同时也是驻地艺术家的 <a href=\"https://www.cletile.com/collections/artist-collection-luca-osborn\" rel=\"nofollow\">Luca Osburn</a> 带来了一套以海洋为灵感的手作瓷砖 Tides。作为一名冲浪爱好者，Luca 选择了灰、蓝、绿、粉四种颜色以反映他心仪的四个冲浪地。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221129ybVP9ODtmFBGScqr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.925000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221129Pc2Yk3e9hO0Xy8iH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221129idSowM1hOecr4yNG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705152211303BJvqL6MQc19s8uC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705152211309himjVAI3kfQZsn1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Fortnum &amp; Mason by Design Bridge</h3><p>提到传统的英式下午茶时，你会想到什么？为了强调精致与复古感，创意机构 <a href=\"http://www.designbridge.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Bridge</a> 为英国食品品牌 <a href=\"https://www.fortnumandmason.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fortnum &amp; Mason</a> 旗下的饼干打造了一套以陶瓷盘为灵感的多彩包装。将铁盒排开后，它们还能组成陶瓷盘的一部分，看似随性地覆盖在蓝色花纹上的六种颜色则分别代表了饼干的风味，有一种微妙的流动感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221147yv4OZLEus3RcA7eF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221148X5uAF9BrkRqnVgZO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221148rMowesD29vA03RJL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221147Gtvf1zKE3ATQrwLe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221147sDeSrw2yZMC6l5bz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Unsatisfying by Parallel</h3><p>你有注意过视频网站上那些题为“看了让人满足”的视频吗？来自巴黎的动画工作室 <a href=\"http://parallelproduction.tv/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Parallel</a> 并不打算追随这一潮流，在他们看来，生活中各种恼人或是令强迫症患者感到沮丧的瞬间也是极佳的创作素材。在这套以 Unsatisfying 为名的动画短片中，工作室描绘了投篮进不去、勺子沉进汤中、加载卡在 99% 等八个不幸的结局。除了短片之外，他们还设立了同名的动画挑战，向所有人征集类似的动画。如果你喜欢这种风格，可以通过<a href=\"http://unsatisfying.tv/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>查看所有作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221213uqIoYScQHhaj8MXC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.746875\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221213iwfOgv7Kd6INkm03.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170515221212w3Je4UVxkS7NgTDt.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.740625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div>"}